# Inference rules for the family.ttl dataset
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/family#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

# Every Employee is a Person (mirrors the rdfs:subClassOf in the ontology)
ex:Person[?x] :- ex:Employee[?x] .
